TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Look up to get scrap_quantity from order_Description table
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SCRAP_QUANTITY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select order_label as order_label, scrap_qty as scrap_qty from (SELECT a.order_label as order_label, (MAX(a.scrap_factor) + SUM(NVL(b.scrap_factor,0))) as Scrap_Qty FROM order_description a LEFT JOIN order_description b ON a.order_label = b.note GROUP BY a.order_label)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Look up to get as_of_Date from day_dimension
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_AS_OF_DATE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
